<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Columbia/HCA upgraded.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Columbia/HCA upgraded.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Stephens Inc said it upgraded Columbia/HCA Healthcare Corp to strong buy from buy.</p>
<p>-- said believes the market overreacted to the investigations currently taking place at Columbia/HCA's El Paso facilities.</p>
<p>-- said believes that the main issues of the investigation concern doctor ownership at Columbia hospitals and Medicare coding.</p>
<p>-- said it is not worried about any long-term impact of the investigatiion on the company's current referral patterns.</p>
</text>
